/>\n搭飛機仲嚴重<br />\n有時落機都keep住痛一陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7d5c0df31d926c1c233aea13e903a83b972c564","tid":352271,"uid":117184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T16:47:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>間唔時會發生，就降落就feel到，降緊落就會劇痛，係痛到裂個隻，所以每次就降落時就逼自己訓教，萬試萬靈</blockquote><br />\n會痛醒"},{"pid":"61abb86b8589a62866746a024af50563e4346be9","tid":352271,"uid":128921,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T17:39:02.000Z","msg":"好撚辛苦，試過反壓，吞口水，但都只係止到少少痛，個頭一擰就極痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05b26f0b00f5e50afd2b58238c849fb0101bcd52","tid":352271,"uid":1095,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T17:50:18.000Z","msg":"先吸滿一大口氣後憋住，將鼻子捏緊並鼓起腮幫子，再以臉頰與喉部肌肉用力將氣吹入後鼻部，有時會聽到「啵」一聲，這表示耳咽管被吹開了，耳朵就通了。"},{"pid":"04a9c51ea84de72fbf266c0950544958648ac86a","tid":352271,"uid":65481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T17:53:03.000Z","msg":"平衡番耳壓就得<br />\ne.g打呵欠，擤鼻"},{"pid":"394739ac8c0e7870444e954022524d2f875bd881","tid":352271,"uid":100760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T18:04:53.000Z","msg":"打喊路，對耳就會通返，不過我又冇好似樓主咁劇痛。"},{"pid":"df95cc58d281c5fccc01c6f17cebe77957dfe9e3","tid":352271,"uid":66436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T19:30:30.000Z","msg":"會勁痛 好似話嚴重得滯會穿耳膜 落機個時食香口膠就得"},{"pid":"305afa587ef6c6c505d302efd4014eaa3c494bc2","tid":352271,"uid":12864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T19:37:23.000Z","msg":"我係前額成個頭都好撚痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我痛到會標眼液"},{"pid":"c7d3dd9dfaded976a481ebf20ddc9c36c3e871f7","tid":352271,"uid":12864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T19:38:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我係前額成個頭都好撚痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我痛到會標眼<span style=\"color: red;\">淚</span></blockquote>"},{"pid":"582cf